CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773864688
OL,3,CGovernment to launch 'targeted'
OL,4,Cmeningitis B vaccination programme
OL,6,FA vaccination programme will take
OL,7,Fplace to immunise students living in
OL,8,FUniversity of Kent halls of residence
OL,9,Fin Canterbury against meningitis B,
OL,10,FWes Streeting has announced.
OL,12,FIt follows the outbreak of meningitis
OL,13,Fin the county, where two young people
OL,14,Fhave died and others are in hospital.
OL,16,FSome cases have been confirmed as
OL,17,Fmeningitis B, health officials have
OL,18,Fsaid, as hundreds of people are being
OL,19,Furged to get antibiotics to stem the
OL,20,Fspread of infection.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773864688
OL,3,CGovernment to launch 'targeted'
OL,4,Cmeningitis B vaccination programme
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA),
OL,7,Fwhich is investigating said it would
OL,8,Fconfirm the strain seen in other cases
OL,9,F"when we have the full results".
OL,11,FThe Health Secretary said most
OL,12,Fstudents would not already be
OL,13,Fvaccinated, and the jabs will begin in
OL,14,Fthe next few days.
OL,16,FMr Streeting told MPs: "From 2015 the
OL,17,FmenB vaccine has been available on the
OL,18,FNHS as part of routine childhood
OL,19,Fimmunisations, but clearly mostly
OL,20,Fstudents would not be vaccinated.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@_O]xD@XOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773864688
OL,3,CGovernment to launch 'targeted'
OL,4,Cmeningitis B vaccination programme
OL,6,F"Given the severity of the situation,
OL,7,FI can confirm to the House that we
OL,8,Fwill begin a targeted vaccination
OL,9,Fprogramme for students living in halls
OL,10,Fof residence at the University of Kent
OL,11,Fin Canterbury, which will begin in the
OL,12,Fcoming days."
OL,14,FThe Health Secretary said his
OL,15,Fdepartment would continue working
OL,16,Fclosely with UKHSA on its handling of
OL,17,Fthe outbreak.
OL,19,FWes Street told the Commons: "This is
OL,20,Fan unprecedented outbreak. It is also
OL,21,Fa rapidly developing situation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@MO]{D@^OU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
