PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773864688
OL,3,CGovernment to launch 'targeted'
OL,4,Cmeningitis B vaccination programme
OL,6,FMr Streeting urged MPs to "stick to
OL,7,Fthe facts" and continued: "This is the
OL,8,Fcurrent situation ` as of 9.30am this
OL,9,Fmorning, UKHSA (UK Health Security
OL,10,FAgency) has confirmed four cases of
OL,11,Fgroup B meningococcal disease, with
OL,12,Fanother 11 cases under investigation.
OL,14,F"The two deaths are associated with
OL,15,Fthis cluster.
OL,26,@nD@[OUoD@JO]oD@[OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
