PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773864688
OL,3,CGovernment to launch 'targeted'
OL,4,Cmeningitis B vaccination programme
OL,6,F"The majority of cases link back to
OL,7,Fthe Club Chemistry nightclub over the
OL,8,Fdates of the fifth, sixth and seventh
OL,9,Fof March and their associated
OL,10,Fnetworks. Club Chemistry is currently
OL,11,Fclosed voluntarily.
OL,13,F"Going forward, these figures will be
OL,14,Fupdated publicly by UKHSA each day at
OL,15,F9.30am."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
