PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773864688
OL,3,CGovernment to launch 'targeted'
OL,4,Cmeningitis B vaccination programme
OL,6,FA Year 13 pupil in Faversham called
OL,7,FJuliette and a student at the
OL,8,FUniversity of Kent have died in the
OL,9,Foutbreak, with others treated in
OL,10,Fhospital. It is understood some people
OL,11,Fwere put in an induced coma.
OL,13,FThe majority of young people born
OL,14,Fbefore 2015 are not protected against
OL,15,Fmeningitis B unless they have had the
OL,16,Fjab privately. It was introduced on
OL,17,Fthe NHS for babies in 2015.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
