PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773864688
OL,3,CGovernment to launch 'targeted'
OL,4,Cmeningitis B vaccination programme
OL,6,FIt comes as hundreds of people who
OL,7,Fvisited Club Chemistry in Canterbury
OL,8,Fon March 5, 6 or 7 were told to come
OL,9,Fforward for preventative antibiotic
OL,10,Ftreatment as a "precautionary measure".
OL,12,FA University of Kent spokesperson said
OL,13,Fon Monday it was taking advice from
OL,14,Fthe UKHSA and communicating with
OL,15,Fstudents and staff.
OL,26,@rD@POUrD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
