PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773864688
OL,3,CGovernment to launch 'targeted'
OL,4,Cmeningitis B vaccination programme
OL,6,FAmelia McIlroy, the headteacher of
OL,7,FQueen Elizabeth's Grammar School in
OL,8,FFaversham, said in a tribute:
OL,9,F"Juliette embraced everything that
OL,10,Fschool had to offer with great
OL,11,Fenthusiasm and joy and her humour and
OL,12,Fpositivity were captivating.
OL,14,F"She was a genuinely caring and
OL,15,Fattentive listener, a true friend `
OL,16,Fwho listened with warmth, respect and
OL,17,Fsincere interest to her peers and to
OL,18,Four staff.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773864688
OL,3,CGovernment to launch 'targeted'
OL,4,Cmeningitis B vaccination programme
OL,6,F"In short, she was a lovely girl ` her
OL,7,Fbeautiful smile, her loving nature and
OL,8,Fher sense of fun will be hugely missed.
OL,10,F"We are all devastated."
